The more I think about this the more I feel like the industrial livestock farming is probably the biggest crime against life in the history of humanity. 
In Germany alone 25 souls are killed per second. 24/7 365 days. 
Around 800.000.000 per year. 
Fisch not included. 
Every time I think about it I tear up. 
How can something like this be still happening in 2020? 
This is a try to inspire one of you to overthink his diet and way of living. 
That‚Äôs the best I can do in my position as an artist. Inspire and lead by example. 
Something that you can do as well every moment. 
grow and give
